commit.message: updated gulpfile and package.json with latest closure compiler dependencies
updated to remove deprecated css-minifier package
Refactored game width and height into constants; disabled turning when mouse is outside game area.
Refactored owner strings and number of construct types into constants.
added dev mode, start using node server.js --dev
refactored UI management code into UI class

game now only sends one request for an image during the initialization of the client. the callback functions in the Game class are now methods of Game and bound using the bind() function added in base.js
updated attribution email and removed Environment.js
changed functions in Game to be of the game prototype and bind them using new bind method
created base.js to hold bind() function
